界仲有咁多人關心我, 我決定努力活下去, 就算最後過唔到呢一關我都無憾, 好感激係呢個post入面留言既每一位, 愛你地, 祝你地身體健康, 生活美滿, 日日都開開心心, 其實健康就係幸福<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa379edfa9925651a5c7b4c8d06c347dff1f0a2d","tid":756182,"uid":51525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T05:03:07.000Z","msg":"老老實實<br />\n吃喝玩樂嘅生活唔會令你滿足<br />\n有咩講唔出嘅說話就快d講<br />\n有對人做錯過嘅就道歉<br />\n唔好到最後半年都諗如果<br />\n搵一班你相處得開心嘅人<br />\n做最舒服嘅事 我覺得已經夠<br />\nBtw 呢度仲有好多人會陪你傾計<br />\n加油巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e7f7afdd80a46544fe0d0d564ad8d7269c52e39","tid":756182,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T05:36:42.000Z","msg":"我應該會去d雪山 沙灘9 hea，到開始悶既時候預約定去歐洲果邊打針安樂死<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18d88451efedbc7545daeab2a3ab796b02e38e44","tid":756182,"uid":102400,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T11:48:24.000Z","msg":"如果真係唔得，要死的話，香港咁撚多仆街，求其㨂過黎陪葬。"},{"pid":"f639a3f51d6f88c22466b7d327071d17d53abdf3","tid":756182,"uid":178187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a2f87fddaab6c0102e2e9fb90e2b63289ad93bcd","tid":756182,"uid":178187,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T18:39:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/www.ettoday.net/amp/amp_news.php%3fnews_id=1023062\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Famp%2Fs%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Famp%2Famp_news.php%253fnews_id%3D1023062&d=jlsdZ6hoUHRkzPCMuPZ9aE%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=ef938d63\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/amp/s/www.ettoday.net/amp/amp_news.php%3fnews_id=1023062</a><br />\n<br />\n樓主可以睇吓上面篇新聞，佢係一個患咗鼻咽癌未期既台灣人，得返10%機會好返，得返幾個月命。<br />\n<br />\n但佢都保持樂觀心態，過著同以前一樣既生活，仲俾心機機做gym早訓，令抵抗力好啲，令化療副作用減少。佢依家已經好返哂。其實有研究証明咗保持樂觀心態真係會對療程有幫助。<br />\n<br />\n但每個人